title: Know The Song Or Get Shocked + Will It Uber: Jenga Edition
itunes:title: Know The Song Or Get Shocked + Will It Uber: Jenga Edition
description:
Bobby, Amy, Lunchbox and Eddie each put on a shock collar and compete to sing all the lyrics to some of their favorite songs correctly. If they miss a word, they get shocked! Also, Lunchbox attempts to Uber a Jenga. The catch is it has to make it to its destination without falling over!
